How is the life of an ece guy in pes ?

hectic. ece is is the toughest engineering course and requires a lot of work. The dept demands a lot too. There are lots of smart peeps at ece.

&#x200B;

Can I get time to study cs concepts and apply for IT jobs ?

Well, weekends probably at the best. You need to learn to manage time really well. Your first year ill be speed rushed. My and my junior batch both had its first year done in 7-8 months.

&#x200B;

And more importantly will ece ug hurt my chances of growth/masters in cs?

not really, but cs students might have a bit of advantage
